                ],
                "institute": "2UK HAR"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Two reactors were used:",
                "  1. DIMPLE is a D2O-moderated research reactor",
                "  2. GLEEP is a natural-uranium, graphite-moderated",
                "     pile, the central regions of which contain",
                "     0.97 in. diam. uranium on a 71 in. pitch"
              ]
            }
          ],
